# SVG Icon System

## Icon Categories & Sizes

| Category | Tailwind | Pixels | ViewBox | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Nav (L1 Sidebar) | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Sidebar navigation icons |
| L2 Submenu | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Submenu item icons |
| UI Actions | `size-6` | 24×24 | `0 0 24 24` | Buttons, toolbars, utility |
| Product Illustration | `size-10` | 40×40 | `0 0 32 32` | Device/service cards |
| Promo / Feature tile | `size-10`–`size-12` | 40–48 | varies | Connect Plus, auth page cards |
| Inline Small | `size-4` | 16×16 | `0 0 24 24` | Chevrons, copy, status, checkbox internals |
| Inline Medium | `size-5` | 20×20 | `0 0 24 24` | Status icons, search, action card icons, row actions |
| Inline Tiny | `size-3.5` | 14×14 | `0 0 24 24` | Shadcn checkbox check glyph, CTA arrows |
| Unread dot | `size-2` | 8×8 | — | Notification unread indicator |

## Icon Sources (Priority Order)

1. **Figma SVG export** — product illustrations, brand marks
2. **`Icons.tsx`** (`/src/app/components/Icons.tsx`) — 90+ custom SVG components; default `className="size-6"`
3. **Lucide React** — supplementary (`ChevronDown`, `X`, `Download`, `ArrowRight`, etc.)
4. **Imported SVGs** (`/src/imports/`) — legacy Paytm brand icons, card illustrations
5. **Inline SVG** — component-specific icons not shared elsewhere

