## Color Patterns

### 1. `currentColor` Inheritance (REQUIRED for all icons)
All SVG icons MUST use `currentColor` instead of hardcoded hex. The parent controls color via Tailwind `text-[color]`.

```tsx
// CORRECT
<path stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" />
<path fill="white" />  /* body fills only */

// WRONG
<path stroke="#004299" fill="#004299" />
<path stroke="#101010" fill="#101010" />
```

**Exceptions:** Brand icons (`UPIIcon` with `#048A43`/`#F57922`, Paytm logo with `#002970`/`#00BAF2`) and fixed-color status glyphs (`FailedFilledRedIcon` `#FD5154`, `CompletedFilledGreenIcon` `#21C179`).

### 2. Duo-Tone Pattern (Product & Feature Icons)
- Body shapes: `fill="white"`
- Detail strokes/fills: `stroke="currentColor"` / `fill="currentColor"`
- Resolved color: `#101010` (Foreground) inherited from parent
- Container does NOT set explicit `text-[color]`

### 3. Sidebar Icon Pattern
Same `#101010` foreground with `white` body fills. Size: `size-6`.

### 4. UI/Action Icons (Icons.tsx)
Simple outline icons: `stroke="currentColor"`, `strokeWidth="2"`, `fill="none"`. Accept `className` prop.

## Component Structure

```tsx
interface IconProps { className?: string; }

function MyIcon({ className = "size-6" }: IconProps) {
  return (
    <svg className={className} viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
      <path d="..." stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" />
    </svg>
  );
}
```

### Product Icon (32×32 viewBox)

```tsx
function ProductIcon() {
  return (
    <svg className="size-10" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">
      <path d="..." fill="white" />
      <path d="..." stroke="currentColor" />
      <path d="..." fill="currentColor" />
    </svg>
  );
}
```

## Icon Containers

| Context | Container Class |
|---|---|
| Device/service card | `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd] flex items-center justify-center` |
| Promo card / Connect Plus tile | `size-12 rounded-[12px] bg-[#e0f5fd] flex items-center justify-center` |
| Circular (success status) | `size-10 rounded-full bg-[#e3f6ec] flex items-center justify-center` |
| Circular (shield / consent) | `size-10 rounded-[12px] bg-[#00b8f5] flex items-center justify-center` |
| Sidebar L1 nav pill | `h-8 w-[60px] rounded-[32px]`, active `bg-[#b1e6fb]` |
| Builder section label | badge on hover/selection with `border-[#004299]` |

## Icon Colors by Semantic Meaning

| Meaning | Color |
|---|---|
| Default | `currentColor` (inherits `#101010`) |
| Primary action / interactive | `text-[#004299]` |
| Accent / brand highlight | `text-[#00b8f5]` |
| Success | `text-[#21c179]` |
| Warning | `text-[#ff9d00]` |
| Error / destructive | `text-[#fd5154]` or `text-destructive` |
| Muted | `text-[#7e7e7e]` |
| On colored surface | `text-white` |

