## Rules

### DO
- Use `currentColor` for all stroke/fill (except `white` body fills and documented brand exceptions)
- Use `viewBox` for scalability — never set fixed `width`/`height` in SVG attrs
- Size via Tailwind: `className="size-6"` (not inline `width`/`height`)
- Use `fill="none"` on root `<svg>`
- Add `strokeLinecap="round"`, `strokeLinejoin="round"`
- Wrap in bg container for card contexts
- Check `Icons.tsx` first before adding Lucide or inline SVG

### DO NOT
- Hardcode hex in SVG paths (except documented brand icons)
- Use `#00b8f5`, `#004299`, or `#101010` directly in SVGs (use `currentColor`)
- Mix icon sizing conventions within the same context
- Use raster `<image>` inside SVGs
- Add `width`/`height` attrs to `<svg>` — use `className`
- Create icons < `size-5` for touch targets (except inline decorative indicators)
- Use Lucide when matching icon exists in `Icons.tsx`
- Import from the `Icons` registry object — use direct named exports instead
